{"tid":1267490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭明晚去紅館賀回歸晚會","createTime":"2019-06-30T02:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T02:03:27.000Z","uid":10540,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36278335915f576a6dcf089e2d68b4306bae3d4c","tid":1267490,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"據了解，政府會按明日天氣和安全情况決定會否轉場，後備室內場地在會展內。雖然政府一直都有此應變安排，但從未啟動過。多於一個消息透露，特首林鄭月娥7月1日晚上會出席慶委會在紅館舉行的「躍動大灣區慶祝香港回歸祖國22周年晚會」慶回歸晚會，暫未有更改。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190630/s00002/1561832167792/%e6%b0%b4%e9%a6%ac%e9%99%a3%e9%97%9c%e6%9c%83%e5%b1%95-%e4%ba%94%e5%8d%83%e8%ad%a6%e8%ad%b7%e5%8d%87%e6%97%97-%e5%85%a9%e5%b1%95%e8%a6%bd%e8%85%b0%e6%96%ac-%e5%95%86%e6%88%b6%e5%98%86%e6%90%8d%e5%a4%b1%e5%a4%a7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190630%2Fs00002%2F1561832167792%2F%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%2599%25a3%25e9%2597%259c%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b1%2595-%25e4%25ba%2594%25e5%258d%2583%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%258d%2587%25e6%2597%2597-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b1%2595%25e8%25a6%25bd%25e8%2585%25b0%25e6%2596%25ac-%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%2588%25b6%25e5%2598%2586%25e6%2590%258d%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e5%25a4%25a7&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=88a0e3e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190630%2Fs00002%2F1561832167792%2F%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%2599%25a3%25e9%2597%259c%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b1%2595-%25e4%25ba%2594%25e5%258d%2583%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%258d%2587%25e6%2597%2597-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b1%2595%25e8%25a6%25bd%25e8%2585%25b0%25e6%2596%25ac-%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%2588%25b6%25e5%2598%2586%25e6%2590%258d%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e5%25a4%25a7&h=d648fcd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/201906